main event: A witness reported observing an unidentified object in Miamisburg, Ohio on 10 October 1965.
interesting points: The object was reported to have moved from east to west over a period of 4 minutes., The observation was made from a hillside., The description of the object included characteristics of brightness and shape resembling a large star., The weather conditions were bright during the sighting., This sighting is part of a series documented by Project Blue Book.
witness description: A civilian observer who reported the observation in a UFO questionnaire.
